data.event: The town once had 2 major employers in the Milford Bakery (manager:Ronald Cunningham) & Flour Mills and McMahons garage, but sadly both are now gone a long time.It now contains a post-office, 4 supermarkets, a veterinary practice, 3 pubs.

The town once had 2 major employers in the Milford Bakery (manager:Ronald Cunningham) & Flour Mills and McMahons garage, but sadly both are now gone a long time.It now contains a post-office, 4 supermarkets, a veterinary practice, 3 pubs.
Celtic F.C. and Northern Ireland footballers Patsy Gallacher and Jamie Heena were born in Milford in 1891 and 1957 respectively.
